freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: I had burning in my chest up my neck and into my jaw.  I also had some tightness on my chest, like when I get bronchitis but without any other symptoms of bronchitis (fever, cough,...).  Onset of repetitive stress syndrome symptoms in vaccine arm.

I suddenly developed high blood pressure after my second dose of the vaccine.  I do not remember if I documented this condition before.  I have been under my PCPs care ever since.  I was at my PCP last night for a follow up appointment.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Burning in my medial mid upper arm to mid forearm and Scilla of arm I received my vaccine.
It feels like a burning sensation in my head, which is not like my normal weather-related headache.  There is also pressure and pain at other times, which is like my weather-related headaches.
Occasionally dizziness which was worse this morning.   I do get headaches when the weather changes, so that could be the issue.
